title: Understanding the Goal
text: The primary goal of data analysis is not just about collecting data.

title: Focus on Decision Making
text: Data analysis in business aims to support decision-making processes.

title: Beyond Data Collection
text: While collecting data is important, the ultimate purpose is to use it effectively.

title: Application of Data
text: The analysis should lead to actionable insights that guide business strategies.

title: Outcome of Analysis
text: The end result of data analysis should be to enhance decision-making capabilities.
